snippet.title: Ball 3D: Soccer Online
snippet.description:
Play here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/485610/Ball_3D_Soccer_Online/

In Ball 3D you kick where you want! Finally, a soccer online game where you have 100% control.

Features:
- 21 Stadiums
- 10 Game Modes
- 100% Control
- Multiplayer
- Realistic Physics
- T-Shirts Customization
- Replays
- Statistics
- Training Bots
- Custom Celebrations
- Best soccer game in 2018!
